OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy in
OL,6,Fthe evening with a little light rain
OL,7,Fpossible. Remaining mostly cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with some more persistent
OL,9,Frain and drizzle for Orkney and some
OL,10,Fclear intervals developing for
OL,11,FShetland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FCloudy over Orkney with
OL,14,Fpatchy drizzle. Drier for Shetland
OL,15,Fwith variable cloud and some sunny
OL,16,Fintervals. Light northwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
