OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Fmixed few days with mostly cloudy
OL,7,Fconditions and outbreaks of rain, but
OL,8,Fthere will still be some drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter interludes. Strong winds at
OL,10,Ftimes Thursday and Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
